Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:32.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,Kidzanira？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:34.68,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：源自Kidzania，日本的儿童乐园，能让孩子了解社会构造与职业体验
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:34.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这可是很受小孩子欢迎的主题公园
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:36.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我好期待星期天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:38.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这种设定漫画中都不会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:40.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你这个漫畜！
